# UI

- Use theme tokens from `lib/app/theme/`.
- Avoid raw colors, spacing, and text styles in widgets.
- Put reusable UI components under `lib/shared/widgets/`.
- Keep screens focused on layout and orchestration.
- Make states explicit: loading, empty, error, and success.
